Kahn: ‘Icecube’ Neuer is world’s best
 
 
He has conceded only three goals in five games and was outstanding in the Germans’ nervy 2-1 last 16 win to shut Algeria out until the 121st-minute of extra time. 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
